# Runtime state belonging to the work-with-me plugin's *sidecar* (under the
# repo's .claude/work-with-me/ dir, already covered by the project-root
# .gitignore). Listed here too so that if any of these names ever appear
# inside the plugin source tree itself — a stray dump from debugging, a
# misplaced symlink — git refuses to track them.
state.json
state.json.tmp
agent-edits.jsonl
